summary: I gotta say, as an 85 baby who was actually conscious and remembers most of the 90s, I think one of the things I'm most looking...
body: I gotta say, as an 85 baby who was actually conscious and remembers most of the 90s, I think one of the things I’m most looking forward to, at this point, from the very high level non-spoilery Captain Marvel early reviews is the fact that the soundtrack is very 90s.

summary: Anche Iron Man, Captain America e company nel nuovo spot di Captain Marvel
title: Anche Iron Man, Captain America e company nel nuovo spot di Captain Marvel
body:
Anche Iron Man, Captain America e company nel nuovo spot di Captain Marvel

I Marvel Studios hanno rilasciato un nuovo spot televisivo legato a Captain Marvel, il prossimo cinecomic diretto da Anna Boden e Ryan Fleck.

Nel nuovo spot le nuove sequenze vengono introdotte da una serie di iconiche scene tratte da altri capitoli del Marvel Cinematic Universe, come per esempio Iron Man, Captain American: Il Primo Vendicatore e Thor.

Captain Marvel è diretto da Anna…
